# 🌐 Multi-Language Translation API

A RESTful API built with ASP.NET Core that provides text translation services across multiple languages using Azure Cognitive Services Translator API.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Translate text between supported languages
- Azure Cognitive Services integration
- RESTful API with simple endpoints
- Configurable with your Azure Translator key and region
- Clean architecture and easily extensible

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

- ASP.NET Core Web API
- C#
- Azure Translator Text API
- Swagger for API testing
- Newtonsoft.Json

---

## 🏁 Getting Started

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/MultiLanguageTranslationAPI.git
cd MultiLanguageTranslationAPI

